OL,3,CFuture of Nissan in Sunderland unclear
OL,4,Cas site closures and job losses
OL,5,Cconfirmed
OL,7,FNissan has confirmed it will shut
OL,8,Fseven factories and cut 20,000 jobs
OL,9,Fglobally in a bid to slash costs - but
OL,10,Fhas not yet stated whether this will
OL,11,Fhit its plant in Sunderland.
OL,13,FThe Japanese car maker has said it
OL,14,Fwill cut 11,000 more jobs than
OL,15,Foriginally planned, having announced
OL,16,Fin November that it would axe 9,000
OL,17,Froles in a restructuring.
OL,19,FOn Tuesday, the group said its major
OL,20,Foverhaul will see it reduce its number
OL,21,Fof plants from 17 to 10 by 2027.
