OL,7,FNissan currently employs around 6,000
OL,8,Fpeople with its factory in Sunderland.
OL,9,FIt remains unclear as to how this news
OL,10,Fcould impact the site, with a
OL,11,Fspokesperson saying: "We are currently
OL,12,Fin detailed study within the company
OL,13,Fregarding the announced plant
OL,14,Fclosures. At this stage, we are not
OL,15,Fable to inform you which plants will
OL,16,Fbe affected."
